Package ohos.nfc.cardemulation

Class OffHostService

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.app.AbilityContext
      • ohos.aafwk.ability.Ability
        • ohos.nfc.cardemulation.OffHostService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILifecycle, Context

    public abstract class OffHostService
extends Ability
    An abstract class that is inherited by the NFC off-host application.

    The NFC off-host application inherits from this abstract class then the Nfc service can obtain the application installation information and connect to services of the application.

    3
